description: Vance has that sweet, boy next door kind of vibe, but he definitely has something up his sleeve. “It’s a different time in my life.” Well, he came to the right place! We asked if there was anything he wanted to show us. “I don’t know. It depends if you can get it out of me…” He got it out just fine on his own, and may we say…impressive!
title: Vance
